OL,3,CSkydiving plane crashes in
OL,4,Cnortheastern France killing all eleven
OL,5,Con board
OL,7,FA skydiving plane has crashed in
OL,8,Fnortheastern France on Sunday, killing
OL,9,Fall 11 people on board, the region's
OL,10,Fprefect said.
OL,12,FThe plane crashed near the city of
OL,13,FNancy at 11 am local time, Yves Seguy,
OL,14,Fthe prefect of the Meurthe-et-Moselle
OL,15,Fregion, told reporters near the scene
OL,16,Fof the crash.
OL,18,FEmergency services responded
OL,19,Fimmediately, and authorities were
OL,20,Fcollecting witness statements, he said.
